        "justification": "A genuinely landmark diff-aware finding: transforms the Sierra Leone/Liberia-specific diamond import bans (EO13194, this stream: 57.14%; EO13213, this stream, Chunk 1: 35.71%) into a GLOBAL Kimberley Process certification-based trade-control regime covering all rough diamonds worldwide - a fundamental structural generalization from targeted country-specific sanctions to a global commodity-certification standard, implementing landmark 'conflict diamond' legislation with lasting effects on the global diamond trade to this day."
      },
      {
        "flag_number": 10,
        "flag_name": "Inter-Agency Cannibalization",
        "status": "NOT_APPLICABLE",
        "points": null,
        "justification": "Not applicable - a single, coordinated State/Treasury implementation with an inter-agency coordinating committee."
      },
      {
        "flag_number": 11,
        "flag_name": "Exemptions Architecture",
        "status": "NOT_APPLICABLE",
        "points": null,
        "justification": "Not applicable - the KPCS-compliance mechanism replaces the prior country-specific exemption structure with a positive certification standard, not a traditional prohibition-with-exemptions architecture."
      }
    ],
    "applicable_count": 6,
